{
  "texts": [
    "GPT-variants predict the next word in a text sequence, enabling prompt-based generation.",
    "For instance, Wang et al.",
    "(2022) compared the performance of GPT-3 in item generation when using different prompts.",
    "BERT was used in 9 instances.",
    "Given BERT's characteristics, BERT variants were employed to predict masked tokens, creating specific item types such as fill-in-the-blank and cloze questions (e.g., Matsumori et al., 2023)."
  ]
}